developer website, as well as

00:35:09.316 --> 00:35:10.536 A:middle
the sample code that goes along

00:35:10.536 --> 00:35:10.986 A:middle
with this.

00:35:11.516 --> 00:35:14.026 A:middle
And there's some fantastic

00:35:14.026 --> 00:35:15.236 A:middle
related sessions on both

00:35:15.236 --> 00:35:17.206 A:middle
localization as well as using

00:35:17.206 --> 00:35:18.386 A:middle
Swift Playgrounds and teaching

00:35:18.386 --> 00:35:19.326 A:middle
with it.

